<html lang='ko'>
    <head>
        <meta charset='utf-8' />
        <title>Been's 계정으로 로그인 오류</title>
        <style>
            body { font-family: 'Google Sans', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; color: #202124; margin: 0;
            padding: 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; } .error-container {
            background-color: #fff; padding: 20px 40px; border: 1px solid #dadce0; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 1px
